item.title: Eddxe - Reminiscing (NEWNAMES Remix)
item.dc:creator: TheRealJFalc
item.description:
I think joining the community was the favorite auxy moment for me in 2017. I had never really known what was capable with Auxy, as I only had dabbled experimentally at best and I didn’t use Soundcloud much. But once I joined for the BTC 14 challenge, I met new people and I began to see how others created music. It was something I know I’ve lost sight of the last month, and I’m hoping to get back to that.
